HA-Gothick
==========

Copyright 2026 HA-Gothick Contributors.

This repository distributes generated font binaries for the HA-Gothick font
family under the SIL Open Font License, Version 1.1.

The generated font is built from the following upstream font resources:

1. Hack
   Project: https://github.com/source-foundry/Hack
   Upstream copyright:
   Copyright Source Foundry Authors and Contributors.
   Copyright (c) 2018 Source Foundry Authors
   with Reserved Font Name "Hack".
   Additional upstream notice:
   The Hack upstream distribution also includes Bitstream Vera-derived notice
   material. When redistributing upstream source materials, keep the upstream
   license files and notices intact.

2. BIZ UDGothic
   Project: https://github.com/googlefonts/morisawa-biz-ud-gothic
   Upstream copyright:
   Copyright Morisawa Inc.

3. Nerd Fonts Symbols Only
   Project: https://github.com/ryanoasis/nerd-fonts
   Website: https://www.nerdfonts.com/
   Upstream copyright:
   Copyright Nerd Fonts authors and contributors.
   Note:
   This project uses glyph data from the Symbols Only font. Nerd Fonts tooling
   is distributed separately under the MIT License, but that tooling license
   does not change the license of the generated font binaries produced here.

Reserved Font Names
-------------------

- "Hack" is a Reserved Font Name of the Hack upstream project and must not be
  used as the primary font family name of this modified font.

